bt.data

Interface DataRangeVisitor


  • public interface DataRangeVisitor
    Traverses a data range on a per-unit basis.
    Since:
    1.2

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      boolean visitUnit(StorageUnit unit, long off, long lim)
      Visit (a part of) a file in a range of files

    • Method Detail

      • visitUnit

        boolean visitUnit(StorageUnit unit,
                  long off,
                  long lim)
        Visit (a part of) a file in a range of files
        Parameters:
        unit - A storage unit
        off - Offset that designates the beginning of this chunk's part in the file, inclusive; visitor must not access the file before this index
        lim - Limit that designates the end of this chunk's part in the file, exclusive; visitor must not access the file at or past this index (i.e. the limit does not belong to this chunk)
        Returns:
        true if next file should be visited; false to stop
        Since:
        1.2
